imdb.plot outline: What really goes on? In this new Documentary / Reality Series we follow a Hollywood based Management company, A UK Agency and the all the people involved it. We see lives evolve as if 'over night' we see the real blood sweat and tears that go into making it to the top of Hollywood. We see perceptions and presumptions demolished and people pushed to breaking point.
